This makes looking for tabs in pull requests when there should be spaces more difficult, as 2 spaces in is harder to spot that 4 spaces out.

It&#x27;d be great to have this just set the tab-size to whatever you enter - I have a feeling this may have been how the change from the default tab size of 8 before the the new 4 was implemented though.

