Atlassian Editor escapes any copy pasted content even if it is in a code block. For example

{code}
#!
~~~~
[test]

~~~~
{code}

would result in

{code}
#!
\[test\]
{code}

h3. Workaround
Open the code block (with ``` or by clicking the button), then paste the contents into the code block.
